reviews.text:
Very average dim sum, and rather overpriced compared to other restaurants in the area. I think they aim to be more premium, but the food isn't special. 

They do trolley service, so you have to wait the trolley with the food items you want to come by and call out for them. Staff friendliness varied a lot; some were helpful and patient but others not so much.

Reasonable price and choice, location is great, easy to find, they are still serving dim sum with dim sum cart which is the most traditional style for dim sum, it also helps to keep food fresh, you can order a new one after finish the old one. Food quality is not toooo bad but not very good as well. **you can reserve your seat before going there from the app - the GULU to skip the queue since it can be quite crowded sometimes.

There aren't enough waiters to serve the customers. There were at least 60 tables and only 4 waitresses. Basically you get ignored. Prices are expensive and the food is normal. Highly disappointed for such a restaurant which is considered as a quality Chinese restaurant!

Came here for dim sum breakfast. Had siu mai, char siu buns, custard buns and 3 mini egg tarts, and it came to $166! The portions were small and I wouldn't say it was that tasty, so we were shocked at how much it was when we got the bill. The service was ok. I wouldn't come here again as it was a rip off!
Good food, great atmosphere.

reviews.text: 老火湯保持水準外，其他菜色每況愈下。即燒乳豬又凍又乾又鞋口，貴族安格斯牛柳端上枱時又係凍嘅，外層煎到焦黑如炭，唔知用乜醃料色澤好似發霉咁，一望就知好唔新鮮，唔敢食落肚。銅鑼灣翠園是美心飲食集團其中-一隻害群之馬。
銅鑼灣翠園都算係比較出名的但到今時今日仍然都如此食物時好時壞唔熱唔新鮮冇水準侍應態度超差白鴿眼叫埋單冇禮貌本人都明白這行有錢比侍應就招呼好的但都不用這麼明顯管理超差推車姐姐居然要食客出去攞食物佢地忙可以理解但本人所見推車姐姐就掛住同熟客寒暄不理會其他客實在太離譜比錢仲要受氣話哂都算係高級食肆所以本人覺得每次幫襯都好似乞求服務的感覺。本人以後就算冇茶飲都不會再幫襯該集團的食肆。

Very average dim sum, and rather overpriced compared to other restaurants in the area. I think they aim to be more premium, but the food isn't special. 

They do trolley service, so you have to wait the trolley with the food items you want to come by and call out for them. Staff friendliness varied a lot; some were helpful and patient but others not so much.

食物只有叉燒酥好吃
其他很雷
by台灣遊客

服務員態度非常糟糕，翠園餐點棒！
但如果服務員態度不改，絕不再去
